      <title>英国将彻底改革电网以加速脱碳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/uk-set-to-overhaul-power-grid-queue-to-speed-up-decarbonization</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国能源监管机构 Ofgem 有意批准该国电网运营商的一项提议，对寻求接入电网的发电项目队列进行全面改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-14/uk-set-to-overhaul-power-grid-queue-to-speed-up-decarbonization</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Feb 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
